						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up at the steps at <hi rend="italic">Bugga-Vaṅka.</hi></p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1639, Hēmaḷambi, Māgha śu. 15, Monday</hi> corresponding to 1717 A.D., January 2, Wednesday.</p>						

						<p>It records the construction of the steps by Kṛishṇājipantulu, son of Śeshādripantulu of Kauśika <hi rend="italic">gōtra.</hi></p>						

